Sentencas: Electrochemical reactions in solid oxide fuel cells take place around three-phase boundaries (TPBs).
Titulo: Three phase boundaries and electrochemically active zones of lanthanum strontium vanadate-yttria-stabilized zirconia anodes in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrochemically active zones (EAZs) are generated in three-dimensions around the TPBs of on-running SOFCs.
Titulo: Three phase boundaries and electrochemically active zones of lanthanum strontium vanadate-yttria-stabilized zirconia anodes in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This work discusses the behaviours of TPBs and EAZs via a case study on lanthanum strontium vanadate (LSV)-yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) composite anode.
Titulo: Three phase boundaries and electrochemically active zones of lanthanum strontium vanadate-yttria-stabilized zirconia anodes in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A percolating binary particle aggregate, based on geometric random loose packing model and traditional sintering theory, is constructed to represent the LSV-YSZ anode.
Titulo: Three phase boundaries and electrochemically active zones of lanthanum strontium vanadate-yttria-stabilized zirconia anodes in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The TPB lengths of LSV-YSZ anodes are evaluated from the coordination numbers and sintering necks of the particles in the particle aggregate.
Titulo: Three phase boundaries and electrochemically active zones of lanthanum strontium vanadate-yttria-stabilized zirconia anodes in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Empirical interrelations among TPBs, EAZs, active electrode thickness, in-depth penetration of electrocatalysts of polarized LSV-YSZ anode are established.
Titulo: Three phase boundaries and electrochemically active zones of lanthanum strontium vanadate-yttria-stabilized zirconia anodes in solid oxide fuel cells
